comments: Had him for Pre-calc 2. All his lectures are on YouTube, and he explains all the topics thoroughly. Am taking him again for next semester!
Mr. Wilkerson is a great professor! I would recommend him and if I had to take his class again I would without hesitation.

Mr. Wilkerson is awesome...he is super nice and always willing to help. His methods of posting quizzes and reviewing for tests will never lead you stray. I was never surprised on a test and I\'m terrible at math!!! Great professor, and I learned A LOT from the class!!!!
